                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-68-off407 t18191201-68-cd408"></join>. 30 lbs. of bacon, value 12 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18191201-68-victim828" type="victimName">
                           Henry 
                           Long
                        <interp inst="t18191201-68-victim828" type="surname" value="Long"></interp>
